Then we will too!
We'll wipe them out inside!

392
00:25:16.200 --> 00:25:18.500
You're not getting away!

393
00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:26.320
Hey, someone's coming up!
Is it the enemy?!

394
00:25:26.320 --> 00:25:27.420
No, wait!

395
00:25:27.420 --> 00:25:30.200
They're the Supersonic
Duck Squad! Let them in!

396
00:25:45.330 --> 00:25:48.710
There's no way you'll escape from me!

397
00:26:04.530 --> 00:26:07.210
Thanks for following us
all the way here!

398
00:26:07.210 --> 00:26:08.420
What?!

399
00:26:11.490 --> 00:26:13.260
Stop! Stop!

400
00:26:14.820 --> 00:26:18.570
You guys have good instincts!
That's right, I'm Princess Vivi!

401
00:26:18.570 --> 00:26:23.730
What's that cra—er—nonsense
you're talking about? I'm the real Vivi.

402
00:26:26.350 --> 00:26:28.800
I wonder if this is far enough?

403
00:26:33.220 --> 00:26:36.870
It's amusing how well you fell for it.

404
00:26:37.410 --> 00:26:38.200
Now...

405
00:26:39.080 --> 00:26:41.710
let us show you who we really are.

406
00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:45.880
– Too bad, you guessed wrong!
– Too bad, you guessed wrong!

407
00:26:49.860 --> 00:26:52.220
What?!

408
00:26:57.870 --> 00:26:59.930
Thank you, everyone.

409
00:27:02.420 --> 00:27:06.520
I have to hurry. The Rebel Army
could arrive at any moment.

410
00:27:07.390 --> 00:27:08.820
Let's go, Karoo!

411
00:27:10.530 --> 00:27:12.190
A camel?!

412
00:27:12.190 --> 00:27:15.450
And I know you from earlier!

413
00:27:15.450 --> 00:27:17.160
S-Sorry!

414
00:27:17.160 --> 00:27:19.160
Go on, Zoro! Let them have it!

415
00:27:19.160 --> 00:27:21.350
You keep quiet!

416
00:27:21.350 --> 00:27:23.120
They got us.
How much was that debt, again?

417
00:27:23.120 --> 00:27:25.330
Quite the farce, huh?
You've already forgiven that!

418
00:27:26.830 --> 00:27:29.460
There won't be a rebellion now.

419
00:27:29.460 --> 00:27:31.050
What?!

420
00:27:34.300 --> 00:27:35.930
I'll stop them, at any cost!

421
00:27:35.930 --> 00:27:39.380
If I don't stop them now,
then this will all be for naught!

422
00:27:41.940 --> 00:27:47.290
Vivi and Koza must not
be allowed to meet!

423
00:27:54.060 --> 00:27:57.300
Secure those cannonballs!
I don't want them rolling away!

424
00:27:57.300 --> 00:27:59.500
Artillerymen, maintain your posts!

425
00:27:59.500 --> 00:28:02.040
Keep your cannonballs
under tight control!

426
00:28:02.790 --> 00:28:04.790
The ground is really rumbling, huh?

427
00:28:04.790 --> 00:28:07.790
The enemy is a force
of two million angry men.

428
00:28:07.790 --> 00:28:11.250
Even the earth trembles
before them. Do not shrink back!

429
00:28:22.460 --> 00:28:25.500
It's okay, Karoo.
You don't have to be here.

430
00:28:28.520 --> 00:28:30.730
We wouldn't want you
to get trampled.

431
00:28:42.630 --> 00:28:47.370
Please, Leader,
listen to what I have to say.

432
00:28:53.380 --> 00:28:57.630
Everyone, stay together!
Charge through at the south gate!

433
00:28:57.630 --> 00:29:00.550
We'll knock out all
the others from the inside!

434
00:29:00.550 --> 00:29:02.840
Be steadfast in your resolve!

435
00:29:11.520 --> 00:29:13.690
Stop, Rebel Army!

436
00:29:13.690 --> 00:29:16.440
This fight is a setup!

437
00:29:19.450 --> 00:29:21.860
Please! Listen to me!

438
00:29:27.290 --> 00:29:29.160
Rebel Army! Stop–

439
00:29:34.610 --> 00:29:37.850
Hey, did you see a person
there just now?

440
00:29:37.850 --> 00:29:39.420
A person? Don't be absurd!

441
00:29:39.420 --> 00:29:42.620
Never mind that,
they're already shooting at us!

442
00:29:46.460 --> 00:29:50.520
Why did they...?
We can't see anything now!

443
00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:56.480
What kind of foolish move
was that, Royal Army?

444
00:29:56.770 --> 00:30:00.450
You idiot! I haven't given
the order to fire yet!

445
00:30:00.450 --> 00:30:03.120
Don't go acting on your own!

446
00:30:03.120 --> 00:30:08.250
T-Terribly sorry about that! My hand
slipped, and it just happened.

447
00:30:27.980 --> 00:30:31.230
Don't back down! Charge through!
It's just a cloud of sand!

448
00:30:32.290 --> 00:30:34.730
No, everyone! Stop!

449
00:30:35.710 --> 00:30:39.190
For the sake of our country!
Make the king pay!

450
00:30:39.190 --> 00:30:40.280
Leader!

451
00:30:50.370 --> 00:30:52.120
Leader!

452
00:30:59.580 --> 00:31:00.760
What's wrong, Koza?

453
00:31:02.250 --> 00:31:04.430
It's nothing.

454
00:31:06.160 --> 00:31:07.680
Was it my imagination?

455
00:31:21.560 --> 00:31:22.870
Leader!

456
00:31:24.860 --> 00:31:27.820
Remember, this is our final battle!

457
00:31:30.330 --> 00:31:32.290
Wait! Listen to me!

458
00:31:34.750 --> 00:31:36.710
Leader!

459
00:31:53.720 --> 00:31:55.730
Here they come!

460
00:31:55.730 --> 00:31:58.390
Prepare to fire!

461
00:32:24.600 --> 00:32:28.380
Bring down Alubarna!

462
00:33:00.890 --> 00:33:01.880
Karoo...

463
00:33:05.590 --> 00:33:08.220
You shielded me...

464
00:33:11.390 --> 00:33:18.910
I'm so sorry... Even after all this,
the rebellion has begun.

465
00:33:18.910 --> 00:33:20.850
I'm so sorry...

466
00:33:22.050 --> 00:33:24.350
But still, I will stop it!

467
00:33:24.350 --> 00:33:26.410
No matter how often
they knock me down,

468
00:33:26.410 --> 00:33:30.660
I can't let something like this
undo all we have accomplished.

469
00:33:30.660 --> 00:33:34.900
That's something I learned
aboard that ship—

470
00:33:36.190 --> 00:33:38.300
not knowing when to quit!

471
00:33:40.700 --> 00:33:41.790
Vivi!

472
00:33:43.710 --> 00:33:45.310
So this is where you are!

473
00:33:45.310 --> 00:33:46.750
Usopp!

474
00:33:46.750 --> 00:33:49.970
We can still make it in time!
Hurry up and hop on!

475
00:33:49.970 --> 00:33:52.180
Right! Hold on, Karoo...

476
00:33:52.180 --> 00:33:54.180
There's no saving that bird!

477
00:33:56.370 --> 00:34:00.760
Come on now! The rebellion
will only get worse! Hurry!

478
00:34:03.100 --> 00:34:06.110
That... bird...?

479
00:34:09.530 --> 00:34:11.700
Let's go, Karoo!

480
00:34:15.990 --> 00:34:19.330
What's the matter? Quickly! This way!

481
00:34:21.790 --> 00:34:24.760
Usopp, prove yourself.

482
00:34:27.110 --> 00:34:30.380
Oh, you doubt who I am?

483
00:34:31.510 --> 00:34:32.340
See?

484
00:34:32.340 --> 00:34:33.620
No!

485
00:34:35.300 --> 00:34:38.410
Usopp! Hey, Usopp!

486
00:34:38.410 --> 00:34:40.270
Eyelashes, wake up!

487
00:34:41.140 --> 00:34:44.970
Oh, Sanji. Good morning.

488
00:34:43.890 --> 00:34:44.970
Right.

489
00:34:44.970 --> 00:34:47.780
Ah, how did our fight turn out?

490
00:34:47.780 --> 00:34:51.310
The part of the mission where we
lured them away was successful.

491
00:34:51.310 --> 00:34:52.280
And then...

492
00:34:52.280 --> 00:34:56.280
it was over in two seconds.
One second each.

493
00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:58.200
Did you even try?!

494
00:35:00.370 --> 00:35:02.120
But Sanji, what are you doing here?

495
00:35:02.120 --> 00:35:05.920
Your ducks came to get you help! But...

496
00:35:04.950 --> 00:35:05.920
I see.

497
00:35:06.710 --> 00:35:08.860
You let Mr. 2 get away, didn't you?

498
00:35:08.860 --> 00:35:09.880
Yes.

499
00:35:15.050 --> 00:35:19.360
Listen up. That freak's
transformations are perfect.

500
00:35:19.360 --> 00:35:24.100
He could impersonate any one of us
and make an attempt on Vivi's life.

501
00:35:24.100 --> 00:35:27.060
If you think anyone is acting
the least bit suspicious,

502
00:35:30.020 --> 00:35:32.530
take off your bandage
and confirm your marks.

503
00:35:32.530 --> 00:35:34.530
If someone can't do that,
they're a fake.

504
00:35:35.040 --> 00:35:40.200
Whoa, taking precautions like that
is oddly savvy of you.

505
00:35:40.730 --> 00:35:43.450
So does that mean
you're that freak already?!

506
00:35:43.450 --> 00:35:44.830
I'll cut you down!

507
00:35:44.830 --> 00:35:46.350
Ah, it's Zoro.

508
00:35:46.350 --> 00:35:48.420
Oh, it really is Zoro?

509
00:35:54.630 --> 00:35:57.840
You... are not Usopp!

510
00:36:00.030 --> 00:36:01.810
Oh, dear...

511
00:36:03.310 --> 00:36:06.770
I wonder what gave me away.

512
00:36:06.770 --> 00:36:09.400
I thought it was perfect.

513
00:36:10.530 --> 00:36:13.720
We got a report that you
all had the same wrapping,

514
00:36:13.720 --> 00:36:17.200
straight from Zero baby.

515
00:36:18.880 --> 00:36:21.200
This is bad.

516
00:36:21.730 --> 00:36:23.960
Vivi is in danger!
